, holotype, China, Yünnan, slide no. GYP4934 (PGM); 8. 
<taxonomicName id="D7DA4D47A942FF84FAAEF8A2A3F1F875" authority="Gyulai, 2018" authorityName="Gyulai" authorityYear="2018" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Xestia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="447" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lanceolata" status="sp. n.">
